Michael Carlyle Hall -LRB- born February 1 , 1971 -RRB- is an American actor , known for his role as Dexter Morgan , a serial killer and blood spatter analyst , in the Showtime TV Network series Dexter , and as David Fisher in the HBO drama series Six Feet Under .
